No openings are currently available, though we're always willing to meet and talk with people who feel they'd like to work for us.  If you're passionate about our mission, talented, and dedicated to learning, get a hold of us and we'll see if a new position can be created.  Additionally, we are always looking for volunteers and you can find more out on the <a href="https://themusecollaborative.org/donate/get-involved/">Get Involved</a> page.

